author: @AdityaVarma-og3tu
text: You might face error at 1:57:23 in sending request as (error message: Unknown key value pair -X does not have valid feature names, but StandardScaler was fitted withÂ featureÂ names)  To overcome above error : In ipynb file  train test split type --> X_train,X_test,y_train,y_test=train_test_split(X.values,y,test_size=0.3,random_state=42) instead of X_train,X_test,y_train,y_test=train_test_split(X.,y,test_size=0.3,random_state=42)  Issue is resolved
